videos.description: Kobe Bryant describes the circumstances that got him to Sunday's Mercury-Sparks game where Diana Taurasi became the WNBA's leading scorer. He also details how he and Taurasi are "cut from the same cloth."
videos.headline: Kobe calls Taurasi's record 'well-deserved'
